title: Utah teacher keeps job after Instagram photos land her in hot water
text:
Utah teacher keeps job after Instagram photos land her in hot water 
Daily Dot Saturday 24th October, 2015 
A teacher in Utah flexed her muscles in more ways than one when she won a staredown with her school--one that allegedly tried to fire her after a parent found her bodybuilding pictures online.Mindi Jensen teaches at North Sanpete Middle School, and in her spare time, the single mother of four is a bodybuilding fitness and bikini model.
